    "rich_text_EAN37a": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_QUck39": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This innovative technology combines two powerful plant-based actives: Fernblock®+, Cantabria Labs' patented <em>Polypodium leucotomos</em> extract with clinically proven antioxidant and photoprotective properties, and ASPA, a patented extract derived from <em>Aspalathus linearis</em> (Rooibos), a plant naturally rich in flavonoids with recognised biological activity. Together, they create ASPA-Fernblock®, an additive complex exclusive to Cantabria Labs products. <br/><br/>ASPA-Fernblock® has been shown to enhance the efficacy of UV filters, supporting more comprehensive protection across the full spectrum of solar radiation, including UVA, UVB, visible light and infrared-A. It also delivers the OptiD Effect, helping to preserve vitamin D receptors under oxidative stress and supporting the skin's ability to utilise vitamin D more effectivtly. </p>"
          }
        },
